trans-unit.target: TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_001<tab>There's nothing left to build now! Surely they could spare a paltry few minutes to come and collect these blasted things...
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_SYSTEM_000_005<tab>Complete 100 stellar missions in Sinus Ardorum to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_002<tab>Good day to you, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! Will you come and speak with me when you have a moment?
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_003<tab>The Cosmic Exploration Initiative has barely taken its first steps. To truly blossom, it needs both your talents and your time!
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_004<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! I'm so glad to see you. Will you come and speak with me when you have a moment?
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_006<tab>I worry that other crew members may be in need of help but are too hesitant to ask for it. Might you keep an ear out for me?
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_007<tab>Councilor Y'adebh's inspection couldn't have gone better. If I find another task in need of a measured approach, I shall be sure to come to you.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_SYSTEM_000_008<tab>Complete 50 stellar missions on Phaenna to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_010<tab>Ugh, it pains me to think of the tasks left unfinished back at the Hub... Is there <var 1A 02 /var>anyone<var 1A 01 /var> who might have a free moment?
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_SYSTEM_000_009<tab>To undertake a new quest from Mumukko, you will need to complete her quests in Sinus Ardorum.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_011<tab>How are you faring, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>? I could always use your assistance whenever you have some time.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_012<tab>Well, if it isn't the shining star who personally attended Councilor Y'adebh! I should like to speak with you again once your preparations are complete.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_013<tab>Do keep an eye out for fellow contributors in need of assistance. I'm sure they'd be grateful to avail themselves of your talents!
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_014<tab>Your tireless efforts continue to amaze me, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. The initiative owes you a great deal indeed!
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_020<tab>A pleasure to see you, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! I do hope you can lend a hand when you have a spare moment.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>Complete 50 stellar missions on Oizys to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_016<tab>I can't help but think of all the work still left to do on Phaenna... Surely someone out there can spare their precious time?
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_SYSTEM_000_017<tab>To undertake a new quest from Mumukko, you will need to complete her quests on Phaenna.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_018<tab>I trust you are well, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. If you have the time, I would be grateful of your aid.
TEXT_CTSWKSMUMUKKO_00956_MUMUKKO_000_019<tab>Thank you for assisting with my little survey. I wonder what the results might reveal?
